Features
- search bar, onsubmit event listen, search by letter, select a player, on click we want to display fetch their info
- Select on the player and populate the stats, populate  a list of players 
- have some form of news on the home page before searching. when page loads (can be fake)
- left side bar for stats. middle player cards right for saved players

event listener 
1) event listener on change (for on change of every letter to look up players)
2) mouseover on a card to expand their image 
mouseout - to reverse 2) 
3) onclick (click on a player their stats pop up) on p tag on player name
4) onclick save button, to save the player from the card 
4) onclick collaspe the stats on the screen.
Want player ID in our fetch

https://www.balldontlie.io/api/v1/players - this API pulls team name and player name position /ID
https://www.balldontlie.io/api/v1/stats - player stats
https://www.balldontlie.io/api/v1/season_averages - season averages 
